  "body": " The phrasing of the question was Solve the system of equations and but we could have also said Find values for and that satisfy both and . Both phrasings are equivalent. The point is that satisfies the first equation , but not the second equation .  The solution satisfies both equations simultaneously: that is, if we substitute and into each both equations, the left side equals the right side.  "
